  "keyFeatures": [
    "Multi-periodic Fourier basis functions for capturing daily, weekly, and yearly seasonal patterns",
    "Cubic spline and linear exogenous variable support with lead/lag modeling",
    "Optional trend term (none, linear, or nonlinear monotonic) constant per period",
    "Sparse outlier detector for anomalous periods using L1 regularization",
    "Autoregressive (AR) residual modeling with L1-constrained sparsity",
    "scikit-learn compatible API (BaseEstimator, RegressorMixin)",
    "Regularized convex optimization via CVXPY with CLARABEL solver",
    "Automatic frequency inference from DatetimeIndex with gap tolerance",
    "Weighted least squares support via sample_weight in fit()"
  ],
